NixOS Install
------------------
boot partition
  boot flag
  fat32
  mount: /boot
swap partition
  swap flag
  1.2x RAM
root partition
  root flag
  mount: /


Post Install
------------------
- delete old nixos generations
    delete links in /nix/var/nix/profiles
    sudo nix store gc
    nixos-rebuild & boot/switch

- create mbsync/gmail password file
  - create gnupg user:
      gpg --full-gen-key
  - create gpg file with password example:
      1. run following command
        gpg --encrypt -o ~/.gnupg/{filename}.gpg -r {username}
      2. enter password on stdin
      3. press enter
      4. press ctrl + d

- import openvpn file
    nmcli connection import type openvpn file {file}
